Commentary Text: Jofra Archer to Hardik Pandya, out Lbw!! Rajasthan review against Hardik! Looks very close but might probably be umpire's call. In fact, it's out. Pitching in line, impact in line and it's hitting the leg-stump. Terrific yorker by Jofra as Hardik couldn't connect his flick. Commentary Text: Shreyas Gopal to de Kock, out Caught by Stokes!! Back to back wickets for Rajasthan. Two new batsmen at the crease. Commentary Text: Malinga to Rahane, leg byes, 1 run, Mumbai Indians review against Rahane! Rohit took his time, had a discussion with his team mates and signals for the review with just a second to go. Looks a bad call though. Rahane was way outside his crease when the ball struck him and the replays confirm the ball to be missing the stumps by a fair margin. He was trying to flick across the line but got beaten as the ball struck him on the pads. Impact was umpire's call and it was going over the stumps
